# Python API (Work in Progress)

This folder contains a minimal FastAPI application scaffold. A more complete implementation exists under `complete/python` for reference.

## Environment Setup (uv)

We use [uv](https://github.com/astral-sh/uv) for ultra-fast dependency management.

### 1. Create & Activate Virtual Environment
```
uv venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
```

### 2. Install Dependencies
```
uv sync  # reads pyproject.toml and resolves deps into the local .venv
```
Or add new ones:
```
uv add some-package
```

### 3. Run the API
```
uv run uvicorn main:app --reload --port 8000
```
Open: http://localhost:8000/health

### 4. Dev Tools
```
uv run ruff check .
uv run pytest -q
```

## Project Structure
```
python/
  main.py          # FastAPI entrypoint
  pyproject.toml   # Project metadata & dependencies
  README.md        # This file
  .venv/           # (ignored) virtual env created by uv
```

## Notes
- Adjust Python version in `pyproject.toml` if you need older compatibility.
- Use `uv pip install <pkg>` for ad-hoc installs without recording in pyproject.
